  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Mix rhubarb, sugar, flour, and cinnamon in a large bowl.",
    "Stir in melted butter until evenly coated.",
    "Press mixture into a greased 8x8 inch baking dish.",
    "In another bowl, mix almond flour, brown sugar, and salt. Mix in melted butter until crumbly texture forms.",
    "Spread crumble topping over rhubarb filling.",
    "Bake for about 30 minutes or until golden brown and bubbly."
